    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi Dei eterni. <persName
                            key="#Princeps #Marquis/duke #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis"
                            ref="#people/3002">Iordanus</persName> Capuanorum <rs key="#Princeps"
                            >princeps</rs> petitione dilecti sui clementer favet. Igitur fidelium
                        nostrorum presentium ac futurorum noverit multitudo qualiter <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">per interventum</rs>
                        <persName key="#Intercessory #marriage" ref="#people/3011"
                            >Gaitelgrime</persName> mee dilecte <rs key="#marriage">uxoris</rs>
                        concedo et confirmo <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/84">Sancti
                            Benedicti</orgName> sito in <placeName ref="#places/109">Monte
                            Casino</placeName>, cui domnus <persName key="#Abbots #Personal_rank"
                            ref="#people/2421">Desiderius</persName>
                        <rs key="#Personal_rank">venerabilis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> preesse videtur, videlicet <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >terram cultam et incultam</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Forests #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >silvam</rs> nostro Palatio pertinentem, que esse videtur in <rs
                            key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Landed_possessions #Forests #Comitatus" ref="#places/571"
                                ><geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/3027"
                            >Suesse</geogName></placeName> iustum <rs key="#Rivers">fluvium</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/2825">Gariliani</placeName>, habentes hos <rs
                            key="#Fines">fines</rs>: a parte septemtrionis incipiente primo capite a
                        fluvio et a termino qui ibi positus est et mensurando infra duas columnas
                        marmoreas ab intiquitus ibi fixas dum compleantur passus centum
                        quattuordecim, et inde qualiter descendit iuxta palude que dicitur Festara
                        usque in rivo qui vocatur Ausenti; a parte occidentis qualiter descendit ab
                        ipso termino usque in mare iusta prescriptum fluvium Gariliani. Et concedo
                        et confirmo predicto monasterio de ipsa silva ab ipso fluvio iusta mare
                        passos <rs key="#Size">trecentos sexaginta quinque</rs>, et qualiter vadit
                        directe usque in pantanum et qualiter divertit usque in rivo qui vocatur
                        Ausenti. Omnes predictas terras cultas et incultas et silvam que sunt infra
                        prescriptos fines et mensuras, mensurando semper ad passos <persName
                            key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus" ref="#people/3024">Landonis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">gastaldei</rs>, ego predictus princeps
                        concedo et confirmo prescripto monasterio et predicto abbati suisque
                        successoribus in perpetuum, ob salutem et redemptione anime <rs
                            key="#parentOf">patris</rs> mei <rs key="#Princeps">principis</rs>
                        <persName key="#Princeps #parentOf" ref="#people/3001">Richardi</persName>
                        et mee. Necnon et concedo et confirmo prescripto monasterio et predicti
                        abbati suisque sucessoribus <placeName ref="#places/4522"
                            key="#Fisheries #Fish #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >turrim que vocatur da Mare</placeName>, que est infra prescriptas fines
                        cum <rs
                            key="#Fisheries #Fish #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >piscationibus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Sea">maris</rs> et <rs key="#Rivers">fluminis</rs> et cum omnibus
                        eius pertinentiis, qualiter princeps Richardus pater meus per preceptum eam
                        dedit atque concessit predicto monasterio et suprascripto abbati, ad
                        possessionem, potestatem et dominationem predicti monasterii et domni abbati
                        suorumque successorum, remota omnium mortalium molestatione. Quod siquis,
                        diabolica suasione compulsus, huius nostre concessionis et confirmationis
                        paginam violare irritamve facere presumpserit, <rs key="#Penalty">centum
                            auri optimi libras</rs> persolvat, medietatem nostro Palatio et
                        medietate prescripto monasterio et predicto abbati suisque successoribus, et
                        soluta pena hoc scriptum firmum et inviolabile maneat in perpetuum. Et ut
                        credatur et diligentius observetur, manu mea subscripsi et meo sigillo feci
                        sigillare. Signum domni <persName
                            key="#Princeps #Marquis/duke #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis"
                            ref="#people/3002">Iordanis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">gloriosi</rs> principis. IORDANIS. Ex
                        iussione prefate serenissime potestatis scripsi ego <persName
                            key="#Writer #Judge" ref="#people/3005">Cansolinus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> in anno principatus ipsius vicesimo octabo et
                        vicesimo tertio anno <rs key="#Marquis/duke #Marca/ducatum">ducatus</rs>
                        eius <placeName ref="#places/2343" key="#Cities"><geogName
                                key="#Marca/ducatum" ref="#estates/3001"
                            >Gaiete</geogName></placeName>. Data quartodecimo kalendas Decembris,
                        anno ab incarnatione Domini nostri Iesu Christi M octoagesimo quinto.
                        Scriptum <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/173">Capue</placeName> per
                        nonam indictionem. </ab>
                </div>
